<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[اجْتَبَذَه]</span>: أي جبذه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span><span class="c4">[ر]</span><a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[اجْتَبَرَ]</span> الرجلُ: إِذا غَني بعد الفقر، قال <span class="c2">«١»</span>:<a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span>مَنْ عَالَ مِنّا بَعْدَها فلا اجْتَبَرْ<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span><span class="c4">[ي]</span><a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[اجْتَباهُ]</span>: أي اصطفاه،<span class="c5"> قال اللّاه تعالى:</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span>وَمِمَّنْ هَدَيْناا وَاجْتَبَيْناا <span class="c2">«٢»</span>.<span class="c5"> وقوله تعالى:</span> قاالُوا لَوْ لاا اجْتَبَيْتَهاا <span class="c2">«٣»</span> قيل:<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>هلَّا اخترتَها بنفسك <span class="c2">«٤»</span>.<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span><span class="c5">وقيل:</span> هلا تقبَّلْتها من ربِّك، عن ابن عباس.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p12"></span><span class="c5">وقال مجاهد وقتادة:</span> أي هلّا أتيتنا بها من قبل نفسك<a href="#p12" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
